Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.97,0:22:53.76,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}O céu azul e a areia da praia me chamam,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.76,0:22:59.81,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}dizendo “não precisa ter vergonha, está tudo bem”.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.85,0:23:05.57,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}Desvio o olhar apressadamente
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.65,0:23:11.53,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}quando você começa a tirar a camiseta.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.66,0:23:17.50,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}Debaixo do parasol, passando protetor solar,
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.58,0:23:22.79,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}você parece mais adulta que o normal.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.79,0:23:26.55,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}Opa, fiquei com sede.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.55,0:23:32.47,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}Quero sentir essa palpitação do momento no auge do verão.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.35,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}Corro atrás de você na beira da onda, encharcado.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.39,0:23:44.27,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}Por um instante, você olha pra trás
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.31,0:23:46.94,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}com aquele sorriso explodindo, e eu derreto.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.94,0:23:53.74,DITF KARAOKE - TRAD,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5\shad0}Minha cabeça vai ficando completamente vazia.
